      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Searching for regex &quot;.+&quot; works better. It wont miss the last line in the file if it&#39;s missing a trailing newline like &quot;\\n&quot; or &quot;.+\\n&quot; will. It also semantically matches what your searching for better, that is, lines with characters."
