    "answer_id" : 6783252,
    "question_id" : 3435581,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Quick and dirty way is to do a global search for <code>'\\n'</code>. You can filter it any way you like on file extensions etc.</p>\n\n<p><kbd><kbd>Ctrl</kbd>-<kbd>Shift</kbd>-<kbd>F</kbd></kbd> -> Text to find = <code>'\\n'</code> -> Find.</p>\n\n<p>Edit: And 'regular expression' has to be checked.</p>\n"
  }, {
